    <article class="subpage">
        <h1 class="top sub-header"><p>How to connect</p></h1>
        <section class="body">
        	<p>
                In this section, you can learn everything necessary about how to connect to and play Salvation Dekaron. 
                Should you encounter any problems while following this tutorial, the technical support board will provide you with solutions 
                and is the correct place for any questions.
            </p>
            <br />
            <br />
            <br />
            <h1 class="header">Step 1</h1>
            <p>Download the client by clicking <a href="{$SITE_URL}download">here</a>.</p>
        </section>
        <section class="body">
            <h1 class="header">Registration</h1>
            <p>First of all, you need a Salvation Dekaron game-account in order to connect to the server.</p>
            <p>It is strongly recommended to include both numbers and letters in your account name and password</p>
            <p>to provide sufficient security.
            <p>&nbsp;</p>
            <p>Create your account using the registration form found here: <a href="{$SITE_URL}register">here</a>  </p>          
        </section>
        <section class="body">
            <h1 class="header">Installation of Salvation Dekaron</h1>
            <p>Download the client: Download Page</p>
			<p>Upon the completion of the download, you will need some sort of an extraction program. (I.e., WinZip, Universal Extractor, etc.)</p>
        </section>        
        <section class="body">
            <h1 class="header">Run the Salvation Launcher:</h1>
            <p>Run the launcher by double-clicking the "SalvationLauncher.exe".</p>
            <p>Once the launcher opens, the launcher will update to the latest patch.</p>
            <p>Wait until the updating process is done completely!</p>
            <p>While you wait, please take a look at the latest patch notes on the launcher.</p>
            <p>If the updates are complete, the launch button will be revealed. Click "Play".</p>
        </section>  
        
        
        <section class="body">
            <h1 class="header">You need these files to connect to Launcher and Game:</h1>
			<p>In order to use our launcher, you will need the latest .net framework - Download following file (If you don't already have it): <a href="http://www.microsoft.com/en-us/download/details.aspx?id=17851">.net framework</a></p>          
        </section>
        
        <section class="body">
            <h1 class="header">Run Dekaron in other languages:</h1>
			<p>There are currently no other languages available with our client. We are an English server.</p>          
        </section> 
        
        <section class="body">
            <h1 class="header">Need help?</h1>
			<p>Visit the technical support sections within our forums, or jump on our TeamSpeak server! </p>
            <p>The Staff Team is required to use TeamSpeak and we offer support there. Join now.</p>          
        </section>
        
